{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.1","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.017.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Bataille entre l\u2019arm\u00e9e d\u2019Absalom et celle de David. \u2014 Absalom tu\u00e9 par Joab dans la for\u00eat d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-18: cf. (Pr 24:21, 22; 20:20.) (Job 20:5. Ps 37:32-40.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>David passa en revue le peuple qui \u00e9tait avec lui, et il \u00e9tablit sur eux des chefs de milliers et des chefs de centaines.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.2","name":"2 Samuel 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.29","name":"2 Samuel 17:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.2","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:2","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il pla\u00e7a le tiers du peuple sous le commandement de Joab, le tiers sous celui d\u2019Abischa\u00ef, fils de Tseruja, fr\u00e8re de Joab, et le tiers sous celui d\u2019Itta\u00ef, de Gath. Et le roi dit au peuple: Moi aussi, je veux sortir avec vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.3","name":"2 Samuel 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.1","name":"2 Samuel 18:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.3","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:3","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Mais le peuple dit: Tu ne sortiras point! Car si nous prenons la fuite, ce n\u2019est pas sur nous que l\u2019attention se portera; et quand la moiti\u00e9 d\u2019entre nous succomberait, on n\u2019y ferait pas attention; mais toi, tu es comme dix mille de nous, et maintenant il vaut mieux que de la ville tu puisses venir \u00e0 notre secours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.4","name":"2 Samuel 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.2","name":"2 Samuel 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.4","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:4","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Le roi leur r\u00e9pondit: Je ferai ce qui vous para\u00eet bon. Et le roi se tint \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 de la porte, pendant que tout le peuple sortait par centaines et par milliers.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.5","name":"2 Samuel 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.3","name":"2 Samuel 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.5","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:5","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Le roi donna cet ordre \u00e0 Joab, \u00e0 Abischa\u00ef et \u00e0 Itta\u00ef: Pour l\u2019amour de moi, doucement avec le jeune Absalom! Et tout le peuple entendit l\u2019ordre du roi \u00e0 tous les chefs au sujet d\u2019Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.6","name":"2 Samuel 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.4","name":"2 Samuel 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.6","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:6","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Le peuple sortit dans les champs \u00e0 la rencontre d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et la bataille eut lieu dans la for\u00eat d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.7","name":"2 Samuel 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.5","name":"2 Samuel 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.7","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:7","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>L\u00e0, le peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl fut battu par les serviteurs de David, et il y eut en ce jour une grande d\u00e9faite de vingt mille hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.8","name":"2 Samuel 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.6","name":"2 Samuel 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.8","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:8","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Le combat s\u2019\u00e9tendit sur toute la contr\u00e9e, et la for\u00eat d\u00e9vora plus de peuple ce jour-l\u00e0 que l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e n\u2019en d\u00e9vora.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.9","name":"2 Samuel 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.7","name":"2 Samuel 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.9","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:9","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Absalom se trouva en pr\u00e9sence des gens de David. Il \u00e9tait mont\u00e9 sur un mulet. Le mulet p\u00e9n\u00e9tra sous les branches entrelac\u00e9es d\u2019un grand t\u00e9r\u00e9binthe, et la t\u00eate d\u2019Absalom fut prise au t\u00e9r\u00e9binthe; il demeura suspendu entre le ciel et la terre, et le mulet qui \u00e9tait sous lui passa outre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.10","name":"2 Samuel 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.8","name":"2 Samuel 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.10","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:10","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Un homme ayant vu cela vint dire \u00e0 Joab: Voici, j\u2019ai vu Absalom suspendu \u00e0 un t\u00e9r\u00e9binthe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.11","name":"2 Samuel 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.9","name":"2 Samuel 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.11","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:11","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et Joab dit \u00e0 l\u2019homme qui lui apporta cette nouvelle: Tu l\u2019as vu! Pourquoi donc ne l\u2019as-tu pas abattu sur place? Je t\u2019aurais donn\u00e9 dix sicles d\u2019argent et une ceinture.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.12","name":"2 Samuel 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.10","name":"2 Samuel 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.12","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:12","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Mais cet homme dit \u00e0 Joab: Quand je p\u00e8serais dans ma main mille sicles d\u2019argent, je ne mettrais pas la main sur le fils du roi; car nous avons entendu cet ordre que le roi t\u2019a donn\u00e9, \u00e0 toi, \u00e0 Abischa\u00ef et \u00e0 Itta\u00ef: Prenez garde chacun au jeune Absalom!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.13","name":"2 Samuel 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.11","name":"2 Samuel 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.13","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:13","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Et si j\u2019eusse attent\u00e9 perfidement \u00e0 sa vie, rien n\u2019aurait \u00e9t\u00e9 cach\u00e9 au roi, et tu aurais \u00e9t\u00e9 toi-m\u00eame contre moi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.14","name":"2 Samuel 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.12","name":"2 Samuel 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.14","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:14","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Joab dit: Je ne m\u2019arr\u00eaterai pas aupr\u00e8s de toi! Et il prit en main trois javelots, et les enfon\u00e7a dans le c\u0153ur d\u2019Absalom encore plein de vie au milieu du t\u00e9r\u00e9binthe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.15","name":"2 Samuel 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.13","name":"2 Samuel 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.15","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:15","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Dix jeunes gens, qui portaient les armes de Joab, entour\u00e8rent Absalom, le frapp\u00e8rent et le firent mourir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.16","name":"2 Samuel 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.14","name":"2 Samuel 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.16","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:16","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Joab fit sonner de la trompette; et le peuple revint, cessant ainsi de poursuivre Isra\u00ebl, parce que Joab l\u2019en emp\u00eacha.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.17","name":"2 Samuel 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.15","name":"2 Samuel 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.17","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:17","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Ils prirent Absalom, le jet\u00e8rent dans une grande fosse au milieu de la for\u00eat, et mirent sur lui un tr\u00e8s grand monceau de pierres. Tout Isra\u00ebl s\u2019enfuit, chacun dans sa tente.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.18","name":"2 Samuel 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.16","name":"2 Samuel 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.18","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:18","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>De son vivant, Absalom s\u2019\u00e9tait fait \u00e9riger un monument dans la vall\u00e9e du roi; car il disait: Je n\u2019ai point de fils par qui le souvenir de mon nom puisse \u00eatre conserv\u00e9. Et il donna son propre nom au monument, qu\u2019on appelle encore aujourd\u2019hui monument d\u2019Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.19","name":"2 Samuel 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.17","name":"2 Samuel 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.19","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:19","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.020,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 19-33: cf. 2 S 19:1-8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Achimaats, fils de Tsadok, dit: Laisse-moi courir, et porter au roi la bonne nouvelle que l\u2019\u00c9ternel lui a rendu justice en le d\u00e9livrant de la main de ses ennemis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.20","name":"2 Samuel 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.18","name":"2 Samuel 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.20","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:20","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Joab lui dit: Ce n\u2019est pas toi qui dois porter aujourd\u2019hui les nouvelles; tu les porteras un autre jour, mais non aujourd\u2019hui, puisque le fils du roi est mort.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.21","name":"2 Samuel 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.19","name":"2 Samuel 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.21","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:21","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et Joab dit \u00e0 Cuschi: Va, et annonce au roi ce que tu as vu. Cuschi se prosterna devant Joab, et courut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.22","name":"2 Samuel 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.20","name":"2 Samuel 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.22","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:22","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Achimaats, fils de Tsadok, dit encore \u00e0 Joab: Quoi qu\u2019il arrive, laisse-moi courir apr\u00e8s Cuschi. Et Joab dit: Pourquoi veux-tu courir, mon fils? Ce n\u2019est pas un message qui te sera profitable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.23","name":"2 Samuel 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.21","name":"2 Samuel 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.23","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:23","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Quoi qu\u2019il arrive, je veux courir, reprit Achimaats. Et Joab lui dit: Cours! Achimaats courut par le chemin de la plaine, et il devan\u00e7a Cuschi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.24","name":"2 Samuel 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.22","name":"2 Samuel 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.24","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:24","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>David \u00e9tait assis entre les deux portes. La sentinelle alla sur le toit de la porte vers la muraille; elle leva les yeux et regarda. Et voici, un homme courait tout seul.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.25","name":"2 Samuel 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.23","name":"2 Samuel 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.25","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:25","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>La sentinelle cria, et avertit le roi. Le roi dit: S\u2019il est seul, il apporte des nouvelles. Et cet homme arrivait toujours plus pr\u00e8s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.26","name":"2 Samuel 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.24","name":"2 Samuel 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.26","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:26","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>La sentinelle vit un autre homme qui courait; elle cria au portier: Voici un homme qui court tout seul. Le roi dit: Il apporte aussi des nouvelles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.27","name":"2 Samuel 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.25","name":"2 Samuel 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.27","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:27","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>La sentinelle dit: La mani\u00e8re de courir du premier me para\u00eet celle d\u2019Achimaats, fils de Tsadok. Et le roi dit: C\u2019est un homme de bien, et il apporte de bonnes nouvelles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.28","name":"2 Samuel 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.26","name":"2 Samuel 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.28","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:28","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Achimaats cria, et il dit au roi: Tout va bien! Il se prosterna devant le roi la face contre terre, et dit: B\u00e9ni soit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, qui a livr\u00e9 les hommes qui levaient la main contre le roi mon seigneur!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.29","name":"2 Samuel 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.27","name":"2 Samuel 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.29","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:29","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Le roi dit: Le jeune Absalom est-il en bonne sant\u00e9? Achimaats r\u00e9pondit: J\u2019ai aper\u00e7u un grand tumulte au moment o\u00f9 Joab envoya le serviteur du roi et moi ton serviteur; mais je ne sais ce que c\u2019\u00e9tait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.30","name":"2 Samuel 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.28","name":"2 Samuel 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.30","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:30","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Et le roi dit: Mets-toi l\u00e0 de c\u00f4t\u00e9. Et Achimaats se tint de c\u00f4t\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.31","name":"2 Samuel 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.29","name":"2 Samuel 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.31","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:31","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Aussit\u00f4t arriva Cuschi. Et il dit: Que le roi mon seigneur apprenne la bonne nouvelle! Aujourd\u2019hui l\u2019\u00c9ternel t\u2019a rendu justice en te d\u00e9livrant de la main de tous ceux qui s\u2019\u00e9levaient contre toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.32","name":"2 Samuel 18:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.30","name":"2 Samuel 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.32","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:32","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.018.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Le roi dit \u00e0 Cuschi: Le jeune homme Absalom est-il en bonne sant\u00e9? Cuschi r\u00e9pondit: Qu\u2019ils soient comme ce jeune homme, les ennemis du roi mon seigneur et tous ceux qui s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8vent contre toi pour te faire du mal!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.33","name":"2 Samuel 18:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.31","name":"2 Samuel 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.33","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 18:33","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.018.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.019.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.18.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Alors le roi, saisi d\u2019\u00e9motion, monta dans la chambre au-dessus de la porte et pleura. Il disait en marchant: Mon fils Absalom! Mon fils, mon fils Absalom! Que ne suis-je mort \u00e0 ta place! Absalom, mon fils, mon fils!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18","name":"2 Samuel 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.1","name":"2 Samuel 19:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.18.32","name":"2 Samuel 18:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.18.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb24d4c59.91430358');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb24d4c59.91430358\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb24d4c59.91430358","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb24d4c59.91430358'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb24d4c59.91430358\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}